    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>指定驾驶员模拟器: 成为街头真正的英雄！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指定驾驶员模拟器是一款以城市为背景的开放世界游戏。在这里，你将遇到各种各样的乘客，安全地将他们送到目的地，并赚取金钱！你的目标是每周向老板支付一定金额。如果失败，合同将被解除，游戏也会结束。然而，如果成功，更多的升级和新机会将等着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚗 <strong>夜晚城市冒险</strong><br>在广阔的开放世界城市中，遇见各种各样的乘客。从急躁的上班族到喝醉的艺术家，每个乘客都有不同的需求，考验着你的判断力。通过让乘客满意，你可以获得更多的小费和奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/b5e2086315d296b36235091dcb6a5513.poster.avif?t=1770466302\" width=800 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/b5e2086315d296b36235091dcb6a5513.webm?t=1770466302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/b5e2086315d296b36235091dcb6a5513.mp4?t=1770466302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💰 <strong>车辆升级与自定义</strong><br>利用赚到的钱购买新车或升级现有车辆。通过外观自定义，车辆将帮助你更快、更安全地行驶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/4da5ac2accc54c51910ccdf989a71924.poster.avif?t=1770466302\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/4da5ac2accc54c51910ccdf989a71924.webm?t=1770466302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/4da5ac2accc54c51910ccdf989a71924.mp4?t=1770466302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📚 <strong>提升技能，做到完美</strong><br>在城市的各大学校，提升你的驾驶技巧和对话能力。通过更熟练的驾驶和卓越的客户服务，你将成为最好的指定司机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/3f7879b33a15ee1392d7b0340a4f07b4.poster.avif?t=1770466302\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/3f7879b33a15ee1392d7b0340a4f07b4.webm?t=1770466302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/3f7879b33a15ee1392d7b0340a4f07b4.mp4?t=1770466302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😡 <strong>艰难的一周，面对严苛老板</strong><br>每周，你需要向老板支付一定的金额。这是一个艰难的旅程，但不要失去希望，继续前进。只有持续的努力和智慧，才能解锁成功的钥匙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/3d56a086b87aefd59a6cf1f86cd6cfcb.poster.avif?t=1770466302\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/3d56a086b87aefd59a6cf1f86cd6cfcb.webm?t=1770466302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813640/extras/3d56a086b87aefd59a6cf1f86cd6cfcb.mp4?t=1770466302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你也可以成为街头真正的英雄。在“指定驾驶员模拟器”中，现在就开始你的故事吧！</p>",
